{"tid":605965,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙法院於世界盃前 決定會否將c朗判監","createTime":"2018-03-26T06:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T08:53:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f9f930102cb1a53ba3eb3f810236d079ffd983","tid":605965,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"西班牙的稅務部門以及檢察官已經向法院控訴C.朗拿度，他被指控偷稅1476.8萬歐元。《阿斯報》報導，C.朗拿度之前曾提出用380萬歐元獲得和解。但稅務部門不但要求他全額補繳稅款，還要求他繳納罰款，兩項合計數目高達2569.3萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n　　而據最新的消息，檢方堅持要求C.朗拿度方面支付的金額不得低於1000萬歐元。據悉法院將在6月15之前做出判決，也就是說，剛好在世界盃開始前做出判決。C.朗拿度積極和解的態度，可以讓他避免陷入牢獄之災。"},{"pid":"57df3f16198b4299e02bf3a1055e8871c5a4ca7e","tid":605965,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"如果坐監，<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙出局=因為冇左丙朗<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙拎冠軍=全體上下為丙朗而戰+丙朗遙遠控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丙朗做得慈善多係唔同啲，點都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5e9be8004ba8abe2378dd9d1c0127d7cf63c76","tid":605965,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57df3f16198b4299e02bf3a1055e8871c5a4ca7e","tid":605965,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"如果坐監，<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙出局=因為冇左丙朗<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙拎冠軍=全體上下為丙朗而戰+丙朗遙遠控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丙朗做得慈善多係唔同啲，點都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"丙朗 我寧願坐監<br />\n唔係又要搵隊醫做大龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4d179b9df34441cd6b2cfdaf24c14e1a2166b8","tid":60596